    "en": {
      "title": "6 more reached Dhanushkodi",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the economic crisis and extraordinary situation in Sri Lanka, 6 more Sri Lankans reached the Kampipadu beach near Dhanushkodi as refugees.",
        "The Rameswaram Marine Police took them to the Mandapam Marine Police Station and are investigating.",
        "Accordingly, it has been reported that the number of Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200bwho are going to Tamil Nadu as refugees due to the economic crisis has increased to 129."
      ],
